<section id="about">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <div class="about">
        <img src="your_image.jpg" alt="Kaspar Trantenroth">
        <p>
            Kaspar Trantenroth is a young German filmmaker & editor with a passion for dynamic storytelling & captivating visuals. Always looking for novel perspectives and consistently aiming to strive for excellence. Born in Berlin, Kaspar started learning the craft of shooting and editing at a young age, creating films under the name Kaboon Productions. 
            Most recently, Kaspar has been traveling around South America for roughly a year. He is now back in Germany, eager to create exciting films.
        </p>
